cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

The paper deals with video summarization, which involves computer vision and machine learning techniques (cs.CV, cs.MM). The approach also involves user preferences and utility, which can be modeled using information retrieval and machine learning techniques (cs.IR, cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with natural language generation to produce summaries, which falls under computational linguistics (cs.CL).
